<p>Binance Coin (BNB) can play a significant role in DeFi applications. It can be used as collateral for loans, allowing users to borrow against their BNB holdings without the need for a traditional lender.</p>



<p>Additionally, BNB can be staked in DeFi platforms, earning users passive income in the form of interest or rewards.</p>



<p>BNB can also be used for decentralized exchanges, providing liquidity for trading pairs and enabling seamless crypto transactions.</p>



